# Architecture Overview

## Summary

Three-VM homelab infrastructure running on Proxmox providing centralized identity management, automated provisioning, comprehensive monitoring, SSL/TLS encryption, and secrets management. Demonstrates production-grade enterprise IT operations and infrastructure-as-code principles.

---

