## Network Architecture

### DNS Structure

**Internal DNS (managed by FreeIPA):**
- Domain: `lab.local`
- Name resolution for all services
- Automatic host registration
- PTR records for reverse lookup

**Service Hostnames:**
Management:

mgmt.lab.local (FreeIPA, Ansible, DNS)

Applications:

git.lab.local (Gitea)
blog.lab.local (WordPress)
wiki.lab.local (DokuWiki)
portainer.lab.local (Portainer)
status.lab.local (Uptime Kuma)
vault.lab.local (Vaultwarden)

Monitoring:

grafana.lab.local (Grafana)
prometheus.lab.local (Prometheus)

**Design Rationale:**
- SSL termination at edge reduces backend complexity
- Backend services communicate via HTTP on trusted network
- Centralized certificate management
- Simplified troubleshooting

