## Monitoring & Observability

### Metrics Collection

**Prometheus Architecture:**
- Pull-based metric collection
- Service discovery configuration
- Scrape intervals: 15 seconds
- Retention: 30 days
- Query language: PromQL

**Monitored Metrics:**
- System: CPU, memory, disk, network
- Application: HTTP requests, response times
- Database: Connections, queries, replication lag
- Containers: Resource usage, restart counts

### Visualization

**Grafana Dashboards:**
- System overview (CPU, memory, disk)
- Service health (uptime, response times)
- Database performance (queries, connections)
- Network traffic (bandwidth, packets)
- Custom alerts and notifications

### Log Aggregation

**Loki Implementation:**
- Centralized log collection
- Label-based indexing
- Grafana integration
- Query language: LogQL
- Log retention: 30 days

**Log Sources:**
- System logs (syslog, journald)
- Application logs (Docker containers)
- Web server logs (Nginx access/error)
- Authentication logs (FreeIPA)

