## Design Decisions & Rationale

### Why FreeIPA?
- Provides enterprise-grade identity management
- Integrated DNS and Certificate Authority
- Industry-standard LDAP/Kerberos backend
- Common in Red Hat/CentOS environments
- Demonstrates understanding of identity infrastructure

### Why Docker Compose (vs Kubernetes)?
- Lower complexity for initial deployment
- Easier troubleshooting and debugging
- Sufficient for homelab scale
- Foundation knowledge before K8s migration
- Faster iteration and learning

### Why Ansible?
- Agentless architecture (SSH-based)
- Declarative configuration management
- Industry-standard automation tool
- Version-controlled infrastructure
- Idempotent operations reduce errors

### Why Nginx?
- Lightweight and performant
- Mature SSL/TLS implementation
- Extensive documentation
- Flexible configuration
- Industry-standard reverse proxy

### Why Split Monitoring VM?
- Resource isolation from application services
- Monitoring remains available during app issues
- Clearer resource accounting
- Easier capacity planning
- Follows observability best practices

